<html>
	<head>
		<title>Yppuna</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Hanna:400,300,200,100' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
		<style>
			@@font-face {
				font-family: 'SVN-Karla';
				src: url('http://yppuna.vn/fonts/SVN-Karla_Regular.otf'); /* IE9 Compat Modes */
				src: url('http://yppuna.vn/fonts/SVN-Karla_Regular.otf') format('truetype'); /* IE9 Compat Modes */
			}

			h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6 {
				font-family: 'SVN-Karla';
				margin: 10px;
				color: #4a8dcc;
			}
			body {
				font-family: SVN-Karla;
				font-size: 14px;
				font-weight: normal;
				font-style: normal;
				font-stretch: normal;
				color: #4a8dcc;
			}
			a {
				color: #fea3a3 !important;
			}
			th { padding: 0px 20px; }
			td { padding: 10px 20px; }
			td.db-mail-body { padding: 30px 20px; }
			.db-mail {
				background-color: #f4faff;
				width: 100%;
			}
			.db-logo-img {
				height: 100px;
			}
		</style>
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<table class="db-mail">
			<thead class="db-nav blue-grey darken-3">
				<tr>
					<th><img class="db-logo-img" src="http://www.yppuna.vn/images/logo.png" alt="Yppuna logo" /></th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody class="blue-grey lighten-5 blue-grey-text text-darken-3">
				<tr>
					<td class="db-mail-body">
						<h1>데일리 붐 비밀번호 재신청</h1>
						<h3>@(model.user.username)님,</h3>
						<h3>데일리 붐 회원님의 비밀번호 변경 요청 메일입니다.<br>아래의 링크를 클릭하여 회원 님의 비밀번호를 변경하십시오:</h3>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><a href="http://@(model.host)/reset/@model.token">http://@(model.host)/reset/@model.token</a></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>
						<h3>오늘도 즐거운 쇼핑을 데일리 붐에서 확인하세요.</h3>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr class="blue-grey darken-1 white-text">
					<td>
						<h4>
							문의 사항 <a class="amber-text" href="mailto:contact@dailyboom.co">contact@dailyboom.co</a>
							<br><br>
							데일리 붐 보러가기 <a class="amber-text" href="http://dailyboom.co/">dailyboom.co</a>
						</h4>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
	</body>
</html>
